  "text": "Several bioinformatics approaches were applied for prediction of the new functional characteristics of proteins with the aim of determination of new network nodes and edges [CITATION_1] . Using the predictive tools one can significantly enrich the database and reconstruct more relevant models. It allows detection of promising drug targets.",
